Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burnin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature's hit 39 degrees today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese summers are so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I give...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn on the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that until Master gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But he {\i1}just{\i0} left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master didn't clean up his snacks again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to clean that up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to move right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Slovenly, the lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Such heat is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If this heat doesn't let up, my {\i1}private{\i0} parts will overheat! {I assume she's talking about her internal circuitry, but "my most important place" sounds too vagina-like to leave alone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we have any cooler spots?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a cooler spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:12.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is endless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:19.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My eternal pledge is only for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:26.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wonder if you're your usual self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll sparkle with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:34.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:44.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The arms of the clock advance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:51.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and with them so does time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:58.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}When you are sad, I open my tiny arms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:04.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:13.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is tender
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I can remember your shape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and that wasn't brought about by a program
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:26.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Let us experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:31.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}the turmoil in my heart together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
