Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.84,0:02:39.76,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.7\c&H0F1115&\blur0.45\pos(120,196)}The Visitor that Comes with the Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:39.76,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur2\c&H31271F&\pos(124,199)}The Visitor that Comes with the Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fr-Freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt nice at first, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My lips are purple! {da fuq}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Such cold is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya, don't fake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,5,,It's... really eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,5,,This atmosphere is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.07,Default,,0,0,5,,Indeed, it is rather tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,5,,I-I don't care! Only kids would fall for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Konjac jelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very realistic creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I've cooled off somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Using a Naked Shinki as the ghost is cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's change the setting next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this? {Kouiu no ha dou deshou}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost story house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that a real ghost might appear while we tell stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started in a countryside village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story still spoken of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A lone elderly woman was doing her laundry by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She heard a {\i1}rumbling{\i0} from upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}rumbled{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bizarre sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever so timidly, the woman turned to face the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she gasped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A fruit the size of a human being flowed down the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she listened closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,she heard ever so faintly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a baby's cries from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman grasped a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and {\i1}sliced{\i0} the fruit open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And just {\i1}what{\i0} did she find?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy born from a peach, Momotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we should've explained the basics first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it gave me shivers, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,May I tell a story next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Heheh, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep the ball rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a time when I lost my way in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While I wandered about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the sun had fully set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The black trees made eerie, chattering sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart swelled with terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a small light from deep within the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I bounded towards what I thought would be my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I found only filthy piles of Shinkis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,each body heaped cruelly atop the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,5,,And with emptiness in their eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,5,,they all turned to stare at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,5,,I immediately tried to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,5,,but my body would not do as I commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,5,,I collapsed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,5,,There was a crash from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,5,,I heard the noise loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,5,,I no longer had control over my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only move my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what I saw was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I am the Shinki living next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Don't scare my screws off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You carried no presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be having fun, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It started raining out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, that flash was real lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master didn't take his umbrella today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We all need to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We will choose one to watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One Shinki can handle that mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Ines, take care of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! Time for some cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do th—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather forecast said today would be sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's an omen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going downhill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, it's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An extra hand always helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we work here next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for someone who lives right next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't seen you before at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We all moved here in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When we tried to greet our neighbors back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone{\i0} was out of their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know the housewarming soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought the raw noodles for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but Master wound up eating it all himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I welcome new acquaintances all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Having friends in the area lets you share advice when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with the close-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never go back on those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go... back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to go against the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we won't meet Master when he reaches the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind bearing, north-northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind speed, 18 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculating direction and distance to station from current location...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know our master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a scatterbrain and kind of unreliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's always thinking about us Shinkis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's a nice master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your master like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask... of my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That slipped out from my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That coulda killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great, Strarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You read the wind with just a 3-meter margin of error!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such calculations are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we reached the station ahead of schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see Master arrive if we wait up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we compete to see who can spot Master first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle? Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winner gets a head pat from Master as a reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we decide that without his permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A... head pat, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Act now, and you'll get a {\i1}special{\i0} maintenance coupon too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master will inspect {\i1}every{\i0} nook and cranny of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still need Master's permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Every nook and cranny...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have finished so quickly without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I should give you a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for this to happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only here by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea, so let's have a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna heat up some Jellycans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall finish this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see him! It's Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He is passing us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought your umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lifesavers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Where's Ines?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning while watching the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I leave food out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We should call Ines to tell her we met you safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm all done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That Shinki from earlier helped me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm getting a different vibe from her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't put my finger on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to help you with your tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You... heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you help me with {\i1}my{\i0} task?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she was just with that Shinki from next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fubuki model we met earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki model?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That Fubuki Shinki next door should be long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from a neighbor a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,5,,Master's shoe strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,5,,Another bad omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,5,,I have a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,5,,Girls, we need to hurry home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What've you been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sharpened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The next door neighbor's Shinki went missing in the mountains a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She should have lost power there a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no way for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, don't scare my screws off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something my master treasured very deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I fell in the middle of the mountain that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Things seem to fall a lot around you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it shames me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That earned my master's ire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and while I scoured the mountain alone in search,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,my charge ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done charging, start moving on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be crazy to enter the mountains in such light gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a lot on my plate lately, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the shoes of the Shinki on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that mountain Zelnogrard have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in good health is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was slightly damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I found this hairpin that I carry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came because you wanted to borrow some tools to repair it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take this to Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and give it to her in my stead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Master told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that she no longer wished to see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your master is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to return after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master told us one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That our neighbor's still waiting for a precious Shinki to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly greet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You stall now of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you still call yourself a Shinki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, we're good here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so go ring that doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought your hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,these may not be much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll graciously accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout using the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's weird, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chatting with the landlord earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that address we went to yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt for your help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I heard that nobody's renting out that apartment right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my master's not {\i1}renting{\i0} that apartment out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's clinging to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever a new tenant enters that apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,once they see Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they all run right back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, wouldn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki, your master isn't a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gh-Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I stand here reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:31.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and make something of a foolish face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:39.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Being more gentle than the wind and invincible like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:44.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:51.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Here in the forest I am lost in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:57.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to try finding a four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:04.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The sun is guiding me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:10.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}towards the miracles of two stars together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:13.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Even if we are hurt on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and ten years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:24.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}this future where I can be with you is what I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will walk on ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not miss the sun's sign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki, we're so glad you were able to meet your master again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but her master's a {\i1}ghost{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a ghost living right next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}okay{\i0} with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then I will love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Busou Shinki. {It's haiku!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you summarizing in haiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,next episode, Ann will be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Busou Shinki:
