Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann turns into a human and goes on a date with Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat?!
